snippet.title: BEEP Game Trailer
snippet.description:
BEEP is available now for Windows/PC. Only $9.99!
Check out bigfatalien.com for details on how to purchase BEEP.

BEEP is a 2d side-scrolling platfomer with heavy emphasis on action and physics-based puzzles. Drive, jump, fly and swim through 24 levels across 6 different worlds. Scour an entire star system and collect anti-matter to fuel your exploration!
